    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the shallot has softened, add the<strong> roasted garlic paste</strong> to the pan<strong> </strong>and cook for 30 secs or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>spicy stock</strong> to the pan, reduce the heat to medium and cook for a final 3 min or until thickened and the lamb is cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>spicy</strong> <strong>lamb & chilli sauce</strong></p>",
