    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> cooked spaghetti</strong> to the <strong>spicy</strong> <strong>lamb & chilli sauce </strong>with a splash of<strong> starchy pasta water</strong></p><p>Mix it all together and cook for a final 1 min or until the sauce is coating the spaghetti – this is your <strong>spicy Sardinian-style lamb & chilli spaghetti</strong></p><p>Tip: Add another splash of starchy pasta water if your sauce is looking a little dry</p>",
